<span id="freeTextContainer13745892836605493007">Wow, fascinating. He had a servant’s attitude. He wasn’t perfect but I liked that he was firm and direct. He did not shy away from putting intelligent men into power with him. He really did have the best interests in mind for our country. Poor guy dealt with many physical ailments. </span>

